window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I’ve never been a Daddy before, but now it’s all I want to be....</b></p> <p>I’ve always thought Kinsey was hot AF, but now that I’ve come to know him, he’s so much more than a super sexy silver fox. He’s kind and caring and so damn courageous.</p> <p>He’s also vulnerable and needy, and it lights me up like nothing else. I know I’m 20 years younger, but I want to take care of him.</p> <p>I want to be his protector, his strong man, his knight in shining armor.</p> <p>I want to be his <i>Daddy</i>.</p> <p><i>New Daddy at 47</i> is part two of a duology, an emotional and yummy romance with an age gap, loads of hurt/comfort, and a beautiful Daddy/boy relationship that ends with an HEA. It also contains themes of addiction and religious homophobia.</p>"; 
